edu.uga.cs1302.list

Interface SimpleList<E>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleLinkedList

    public interface SimpleList<E>
    This class provides a simple generic list interface, similar to Java's List interface, but much simpler. The first element of the list is at position 0 and the last element is at position list.size() - 1.
